  "title": "Freelance Video Editor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Title: Freelance Video Editor</strong></p><p><strong>Location:</strong> Remote</p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p>We are seeking a talented Freelance Video Editor to join our team on a project basis. As a Video Editor, you will be responsible for extracting specific segments from our raw footage and editing them into cohesive and engaging videos. The ideal candidate will have a keen eye for detail, creativity, and proficiency in video editing software.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>Review raw footage and identify key segments for editing.</p><p>Trim and splice footage to create seamless transitions.</p><p>Add visual effects, graphics, and audio enhancements as needed.</p><p>Ensure videos adhere to brand guidelines and specifications.</p><p>Collaborate with the team to brainstorm and execute creative ideas.</p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>Proven experience as a video editor or similar role.</p><p>Strong understanding of video composition, timing, and storytelling.</p><p>Excellent attention to detail and organizational skills.</p><p>Ability to work independently and meet deadlines.</p><p>Strong communication and collaboration skills.</p><p>A portfolio of past work demonstrating editing skills and creativity.</p><p><strong>Salary: </strong>$500-$1000 per month</p><p><strong>Note:</strong></p><p>This is a freelance position with the potential for ongoing projects based on performance and project availability. If you're passionate about video editing and ready to take on exciting projects, we'd love to hear from you!</p><p>Students are welcome to apply. We look forward to reviewing your application!</p>",
